    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【玫瑰战争】赛季正式上线！重返1461，加入兰开斯特与约克的宿命对决！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【新赛季核心内容】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新武器·长剑：</strong> 全甲胄通用（轻/中/重甲均适配），连招千变万化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新兵团·不列颠敕令长弓手：</strong> 超远射程+无视地形抛射。无需赛季挑战，消耗战功直接解锁！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双4星·新兵团：</strong> 首个可下马作战骑兵【白玫瑰亲卫骑士】&amp; 拒马自愈步兵【红玫瑰钩镰卫队】。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新地图·阿尼克堡：</strong> 品质全面升级的新攻城战地图，重现史诗要塞争夺。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【新人入坑·海量福利】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开局送大军：</strong> 创建角色直接送 <strong>13支主力兵团</strong>，0成本起步。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试错0成本：</strong> 200级前，属性点、技能点等<strong>无限免费重置</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>抱大腿模式：</strong> 师徒系统上线，萌新可<strong>免费借用</strong>教官的满级满配兵团，出师再送<strong>五星兵团自选箱</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每周限免：</strong> 每周免费体验一队满级、满潜能顶配兵团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/ca28007425458bf50f9210e706aafb07.avif?t=1767008199\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【老兵回归·史上最强减负】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>肝度大砍：</strong> 围城平匪取消场次限制，改为“奖励总量上限”，不论战场表现高低，都能稳定领满每周的经验与声望奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>兵谱减负：</strong> 地中海系列赛季兵团改为<strong>战功直接解锁</strong>，无需再肝旧赛季任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回归好礼：</strong> “英雄之路”重置，海量手札、锻兵令等你拿。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带徒收益：</strong> 成为教官传授战术，赢取<strong>传说器械（神火飞鸦）与史诗武将图纸</strong>。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《战意》——多文明古战场即时战术战争游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为传奇将军，在史诗级的多文明PvP攻城战中带领着你的兵团一起驰骋古战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你是规模庞大的攻城战粉丝，残酷激烈的动作战斗爱好者，还是喜好实时战略的游戏玩家，《战意》都将为你提供无与伦比的战争体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/61af2f392b5a31bd73b235379d8cd971.poster.avif?t=1767008199\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/61af2f392b5a31bd73b235379d8cd971.webm?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/61af2f392b5a31bd73b235379d8cd971.mp4?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多文明古战场：不同文明的古战场战争体验</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《战意》中，游戏以多文明古战场为舞台，构建多张风格迥异的动态地形，涵盖斯巴达的温泉关、丝绸之路上沙暴肆虐的戈壁、日本战国夜袭火攻的竹林城寨等。不同文明的经典古战场供将军们体验历史名战役带来的紧张与刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/32e7b5a12db977d72c10b43a1e6afda1.poster.avif?t=1767008199\" width=400 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/32e7b5a12db977d72c10b43a1e6afda1.webm?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/32e7b5a12db977d72c10b43a1e6afda1.mp4?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>立体化攻城战：策略与战术的终极试炼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验千人同屏的古战场攻城战：操纵投石机轰击城墙缺口，架设云梯突破箭塔封锁，或是率领重装步兵在瓮城展开白刃拉锯。战场设计融入真实军事工事逻辑——每场战役包含攻城器械搭建、阵线推进、据点争夺等，三阶段攻防转换带来全然不同的战术体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/9d7c2c83604a57f00e048b92369014b0.poster.avif?t=1767008199\" width=426 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/9d7c2c83604a57f00e048b92369014b0.webm?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/9d7c2c83604a57f00e048b92369014b0.mp4?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>指挥兵团：百种历史精锐的战术交响</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内有一百多个来自真实历史的兵团，包括斯巴达、维京人、骑士、中国王朝、武士、翼骑兵、近卫军、刺客等供玩家选择，您可以带领不同文明的兵团进行战场体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用独特的兵团技能，如治疗、冲锋、支撑、增益，和爆炸物获得优势。我们会持续更新新的单位和地图，你需要不断调整你的战术才能主导战场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/bc1e28431a4d8146eef13b92d83b3b1c.poster.avif?t=1767008199\" width=426 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/bc1e28431a4d8146eef13b92d83b3b1c.webm?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/835570/extras/bc1e28431a4d8146eef13b92d83b3b1c.mp4?t=1767008199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全球电竞赛事：全球战争爱好者的竞技舞台</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全球性战争爱好者的同场竞技战场“战意联赛（CBL）”，这是一场属于《战意》的年度全球赛事，拥有超过1000位的参与者和价值数万美元的奖金池。向巅峰进发，赢得属于你的荣耀！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>性能：低配置高优化，战斗帧率稳定</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优秀的引擎开发能力，在低配置的环境下，千人战场依然能有稳定的帧率表现，让你更好地体验激情的战争氛围。</p>",
